snippet.title: Moon Watch Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Moon Watch is a Time-Stop Horde Survival Roguelike! Build your deck. Stop the flow of time: think strategically, set up devastating combos, weave impossible odds in your favor. 

Play now on Itch:
https://thejaspel.itch.io/moonwatch

Wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2878030/Moon_Watch/
